## Background and Motivation

We added support for `DiagnosticSuppressor` API some time back. This work added a new internal type `ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo` and an internal property `Diagnostic.ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo` to the compiler layer. This issue proposes making these two APIs public, without any changes or additions to the implementation.

**Motivation:**
1. Testing support: From @sharwell:
      > We need this public API for `DiagnosticSuppressor` unit testing support in the Microsoft.CodeAnalysis.Testing SDK. We tried two other approaches using public APIs but they caused problems for various edge cases. The library now uses the current property via reflection, which is fragile.

2. Tooling support: Tools built on top of Microsoft.CodeAnalysis that require to read/operate on the programmatic suppressions from `DiagnosticSuppressors` would need this public API. 

## Proposed API

### Existing internal type [ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo](https://github.com/dotnet/roslyn/blob/main/src/Compilers/Core/Portable/Diagnostic/ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo.cs) to be made public:

```diff
namespace Microsoft.CodeAnalysis.Diagnostics
{
+     public sealed class ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo : IEquatable<ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo?>
+     {
+        public bool Equals(ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo? other);
+        public overrides bool Equals(object? other);
+        public overrides int GetHashCode();
+     }
}
```

### Existing internal property [Diagnostic.ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo](https://github.com/dotnet/roslyn/blob/86156faa88860dac9b17223623743aea24814291/src/Compilers/Core/Portable/Diagnostic/Diagnostic.cs#L474) to be made public:

```diff
namespace Microsoft.CodeAnalysis
{
      public abstract class Diagnostic
      {
+        public virtual ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo? ProgrammaticSuppressionInfo { get; };
      }
}
```

**NOTE:** `Diagnostic` type has internal abstract methods, and hence cannot be sub-typed outside the compiler layer: https://github.com/dotnet/roslyn/blob/86156faa88860dac9b17223623743aea24814291/src/Compilers/Core/Portable/Diagnostic/Diagnostic.cs#L448-L461
```
